<item>
            <title>[SPARK-4595] Spark MetricsServlet is not worked because of initialization ordering</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-4595</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Web UI is initialized before MetricsSystem is started, at that time MetricsSerlvet is not yet created, which will make MetricsServlet fail to register  into web UI. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead MetricsServlet handler should be added to the web UI after MetricsSystem is started.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
